  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Analyzing the VoiceInput Module**\n\nI\'m truly impressed by this VoiceInput module. Its use of native HTML5 SpeechRecognition for seamless wave feedback is ingenious. The error-handling with instructions and the dedicated simulate system, which cleverly manages device permission blocks, demonstrate a high level of engineering prowess!\n\n\n**Designing the AudioPlayer**\n\nI\'m now completely focused on designing the AudioPlayer component in `/src/components/AudioPlayer.tsx`. I\'ll be using `window.speechSynthesis` and `window.SpeechSynthesisUtterance`. It\'ll take steps as a `string[]` or `FirstAidGuide`, handle play/pause/stop functionality, and will automatically advance to the next step once each is spoken. Crucially, the UI will highlight the current spoken step for a voice-guided experience.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 13
      nanos: 884493282
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
