  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Sleek Interface\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sleek Interface\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex flex-col font-sans text-slate-900 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Section -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-20 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-8 flex items-center justify-between flex-shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white\\\">\\n        <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-6 w-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n          <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6\\\" />\\n        </svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-blue-900\\\">Quick Aid</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-lg\\\">WHO Database v2.4</button>\\n      <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-red-200 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Emergency SOS</button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Main App View -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex p-8 gap-8\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Sidebar: Search and Selection -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Search Area -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <label class=\\\"block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2 tracking-widest\\\">Search Emergency</label>\\n        <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n          <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Describe symptoms...\\\" class=\\\"w-full pl-4 pr-12 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 text-blue-600\\\">\\n            <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-6 w-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n              <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-7-4a7 7 0 1114 0 7 7 0 01-14 0z\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Common Emergencies -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-4 tracking-widest\\\">Common Scenarios</h2>\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 group-hover:bg-orange-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\224\245</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Burns</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-blue-600 border border-transparent rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-200\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-white\\\">\360\237\245\250</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\\\">Choking</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-red-500 group-hover:bg-red-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\251\270</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Bleeding</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 group-hover:bg-slate-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\246\264</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Fracture</span>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- GPS Nearby Hospitals -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-4 text-white flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Nearby Support</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">3 Hospitals Found</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-blue-400\\\">\\n          <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-4 w-4\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 20 20\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n            <path fill-rule=\\\"evenodd\\\" d=\\\"M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z\\\" clip-rule=\\\"evenodd\\\" />\\n          </svg>\\n          OPEN MAPS\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Sidebar: First Aid Instructions -->\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl flex flex-col overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-slate-100 flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <div class=\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse\\\"></span> Active Guidance\\n          </div>\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Choking Treatment</h2>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-slate-500 mt-1 italic\\\">Source: World Health Organization (WHO) Protocols</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 group\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all\\\">\\n            <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-8 w-8\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n              <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072m2.828-9.9a9 9 0 010 12.728M5.586 15H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h1.586l4.707-4.707C10.923 3.663 12 4.109 12 5v14c0 .891-1.077 1.337-1.707.707L5.586 15z\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-600\\\">VOICE ON</span>\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-6 overflow-y-auto max-h-[400px] pr-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">01</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Encourage Coughing</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\\\">If the person is breathing or coughing, encourage them to continue. Do not intervene yet unless they stop breathing.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">02</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Back Blows</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\\\">Lean the person forward. Give 5 sharp blows between their shoulder blades with the heel of your hand.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">03</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-600\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-blue-900\\\">Abdominal Thrusts</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-blue-800 leading-relaxed font-medium\\\">Stand behind them. Put your arms around their waist. Pull inwards and upwards 5 times. (Heimlich Maneuver)</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Progress / Footer within card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"h-2 w-48 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full w-2/3 bg-blue-600\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500\\\">STEP 3 OF 5</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-slate-200 font-bold rounded-lg text-sm\\\">PREV</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-lg text-sm\\\">NEXT STEP</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Bottom Navigation -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-16 bg-white border-t border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-12 flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner\\\">\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-bold border-b-2 border-blue-600 h-full px-4\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6\\\" /></svg>\\n      Assistant\\n    </button>\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 font-bold h-full px-4 hover:text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\\\" /><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\\\" /></svg>\\n      Hospitals\\n    </button>\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 font-bold h-full px-4 hover:text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253\\\" /></svg>\\n      Training\\n    </button>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Sleek Interface\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sleek Interface\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex flex-col font-sans text-slate-900 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Section -->\\n  <header class=\\\"h-20 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-8 flex items-center justify-between flex-shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white\\\">\\n        <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-6 w-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n          <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6\\\" />\\n        </svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-blue-900\\\">Quick Aid</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-lg\\\">WHO Database v2.4</button>\\n      <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-red-200 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Emergency SOS</button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <!-- Main App View -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex p-8 gap-8\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Sidebar: Search and Selection -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Search Area -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <label class=\\\"block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2 tracking-widest\\\">Search Emergency</label>\\n        <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n          <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Describe symptoms...\\\" class=\\\"w-full pl-4 pr-12 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 text-blue-600\\\">\\n            <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-6 w-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n              <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-7-4a7 7 0 1114 0 7 7 0 01-14 0z\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Common Emergencies -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-4 tracking-widest\\\">Common Scenarios</h2>\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 group-hover:bg-orange-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\224\245</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Burns</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-blue-600 border border-transparent rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-200\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-white\\\">\360\237\245\250</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\\\">Choking</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-red-500 group-hover:bg-red-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\251\270</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Bleeding</span>\\n          </button>\\n          <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500 shadow-sm group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-slate-50 rounded-full mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 group-hover:bg-slate-500 group-hover:text-white\\\">\360\237\246\264</div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Fracture</span>\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- GPS Nearby Hospitals -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-4 text-white flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\\\">Nearby Support</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">3 Hospitals Found</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-blue-400\\\">\\n          <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-4 w-4\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 20 20\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n            <path fill-rule=\\\"evenodd\\\" d=\\\"M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z\\\" clip-rule=\\\"evenodd\\\" />\\n          </svg>\\n          OPEN MAPS\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Sidebar: First Aid Instructions -->\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl flex flex-col overflow-hidden\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-8 border-b border-slate-100 flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <div class=\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse\\\"></span> Active Guidance\\n          </div>\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Choking Treatment</h2>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-slate-500 mt-1 italic\\\">Source: World Health Organization (WHO) Protocols</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1 group\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all\\\">\\n            <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-8 w-8\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\">\\n              <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072m2.828-9.9a9 9 0 010 12.728M5.586 15H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h1.586l4.707-4.707C10.923 3.663 12 4.109 12 5v14c0 .891-1.077 1.337-1.707.707L5.586 15z\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-600\\\">VOICE ON</span>\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-6 overflow-y-auto max-h-[400px] pr-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">01</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Encourage Coughing</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\\\">If the person is breathing or coughing, encourage them to continue. Do not intervene yet unless they stop breathing.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">02</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Back Blows</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\\\">Lean the person forward. Give 5 sharp blows between their shoulder blades with the heel of your hand.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0\\\">03</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-600\\\">\\n              <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-blue-900\\\">Abdominal Thrusts</h3>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-blue-800 leading-relaxed font-medium\\\">Stand behind them. Put your arms around their waist. Pull inwards and upwards 5 times. (Heimlich Maneuver)</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Progress / Footer within card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"p-6 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"h-2 w-48 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"h-full w-2/3 bg-blue-600\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500\\\">STEP 3 OF 5</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-3\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-slate-200 font-bold rounded-lg text-sm\\\">PREV</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-lg text-sm\\\">NEXT STEP</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Bottom Navigation -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-16 bg-white border-t border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-12 flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner\\\">\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-bold border-b-2 border-blue-600 h-full px-4\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6\\\" /></svg>\\n      Assistant\\n    </button>\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 font-bold h-full px-4 hover:text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\\\" /><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\\\" /></svg>\\n      Hospitals\\n    </button>\\n    <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 font-bold h-full px-4 hover:text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" class=\\\"h-5 w-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253\\\" /></svg>\\n      Training\\n    </button>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
