on selection in `App.tsx` and have added icons for fracture (\"\360\237\246\264\" or \"\360\237\251\271\"), heart-attack (\"\360\237\253\200\" or \"\342\232\241\"), heatstroke (\"\342\230\200\357\270\217\"), poisoning (\"\360\237\247\252\" or \"\342\232\240\357\270\217\"), and electric-shock (\"\342\232\241\" or \"\360\237\224\214\"). I\'m prepping a complete replacement for the `App.tsx` layout return, from line 138 to 549, and am focusing on building out the new elegant layout. I am integrating a fixed header and implementing the left and right sidebars as previously determined.\n\n\n"
