v>\n                  <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1 mt-1.5\">\n                    {syncQueue.map((item, idx) => (\n                      <span\n                        key={idx}\n                        className=\"bg-white text-amber-900 border border-amber-200/40 text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md font-medium\"\n                      >\n                        {item}\n                      </span>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>"
